  <brief_title>Stenting and Resection for Stage IV Colorectal Cancer Endoscopic Stenting and Colorectal Resection in Stage IV</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison Between Endoscopic Stenting and Colorectal Resection in Patients With Stage IV Colorectal Cancer</official_title>
